reviewText: Don't be fooled - Season 3 does not follow the format of Seasons 1 and 2. It is really falsely advertised as a continuation of the series. I would be very careful of buying this. Shame!

Saw this TV series on Netflix and loved it because it was not ugly depiction of ladies who worked in a brothel. Each character has depth and a story-line that is not so far fetched. I wish that the series was offered in a box set and one that you could watch on american dvd machines since some of the dvds sold here are not compatible.
